Path: Nushell
Content:
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14478] upgraded to polars 0.44
132ikl 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14477] improved try/catch errors
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14475] made length only operate on supported input types
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14476] removed unused 
``FlatShape``
s 
``And``
/
``Or``
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14473] updated the Rust toolchain to rust 1.81.0
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14423] removed 
``terminal_size``
 crate from several places
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14418] started to add WASM support again
paulie4 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14468] added more 
``less``
 key bindings and added 
``Transition::None``
 to 
``explore``
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14467] allowed inherited environment variables
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14461] updated default-files README
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14455] bumped reedline to current main
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14439] added example for PROMPT_COMMAND_RIGHT
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14436] removed long-unused 
``autoenv``
 tests
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14435] ensured config record is always populated during startup
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14319] deprecated 
``date to-record``
 and 
``date to-table``
WindSoilder 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14456] updated unicode-width to 0.2
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14454] updated miette to 7.3
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14405] raised a ParseError if assigning to a non-variable or non-mutable-variable
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14385] deprecated --ignore-shell-errors and --ignore-program-errors in 
``do``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14347] made 
``std help``
 more user friendly
Bahex 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14453] propagated existing errors in 
``insert``
 and 
``merge``
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14427] added 
``term query``
, for querying information from terminals
PegasusPlusUS 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14451] fixed an unstable test case
IanManske 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14425] removed the obsolete 
``ListStream``
 type
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14369] added a 
``Filesize``
 type
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14345] made 
``Hooks``
 fields non-optional to match the new config defaults
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14344] changed append operator to concatenation operator
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14424] fixed: Respect sort in custom completions
cosineblast 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14410] implemented chunk_by operation
amtoine 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14334] added 
``from ndnuon``
 and 
``to ndnuon``
 to stdlib
DziubaMaksym 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/14465] fixed a README link
